    "Anterior segment examination was unremarkable, and fundus examination demonstrated bilateral Frisen grade 4 optic disc swelling.",
    "Humphrey visual field 24-2 showed a few nasal missed spots in both eyes, with an enlarged blind spot in the left eye.",
    "The OCT of the retinal nerve fiber layer demonstrated thickening in both eyes, with average values of 338 microns in the right eye and 399 in the left eye.",
